# Trading Bot — mandatory reads for agents

Before editing files, running project commands, or executing queue tasks in this repository:

1. Read `README.md` in full (project overview and quick start).
2. Read `AGENTS.md` in full at the start of **every** agent session or new thread. `AGENTS.md` is the binding contract; re-read it after any context reset.

Do not skip these steps in favor of prior memory.
